          <h1>上海交通大学“四项举措”发挥学联引领作用</h1>
          <div class="msgbar">发布时间： 2011-06-07; </div>
          
          <div class="content">
         <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;&#xd;&#xa;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">在&ldquo;五四&rdquo;运动九十周年、交通大学学生联合会诞生九十周年之际，上海交通大学第</span><span lang="EN-US">26</span><span style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;&#xd;&#xa;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">次学生代表大会于</span><span lang="EN-US">4</span><span style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&#xd;&#xa;&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">月</span><span lang="EN-US">26</span><span style="font-family:&#xd;&#xa;宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">日隆重召开。这次大会不仅是对过去三年来交大学联工作的系统总结，也是对</span><span lang="EN-US">1919</span><span style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;&#xd;&#xa;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">年至今交大学联创立</span><span lang="EN-US">90</span><span style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&#xd;&#xa;&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">年历史的一次全面回顾。</span><span lang="EN-US"> </span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;&#xd;&#xa;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">交大学联在九十载的光辉历程中，始终与祖国和民族的发展同呼吸共命运，始终紧扣时代主题和校园民生踏实作为，始终走在爱国学生运动和学生组织建设的最前列，形成了&ldquo;勇于担当，善于作为，勤于奋进&rdquo;的优秀作风。近年来，学生联合会更是带领广大学生积极参与到学校建设管理中，为学校的发展建言献策，为学校早日建成世界一流大学贡献力量，在工作中形成了鲜明的特色。</span><span lang="EN-US"> </span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;&#xd;&#xa;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">三联融合，资源优化与效率提升均成效显著。</span><span lang="EN-US">2006</span><span style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;&#xd;&#xa;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">年</span><span lang="EN-US">9</span><span style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&#xd;&#xa;&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">月，原上海交通大学学生联合会、研究生联合会、社团联合会强强联合，合并成立了国内高校首个&ldquo;大学联&rdquo;模式的学生联合会。三联融合对于纵向整合研究生与本科生资源、横向整合各院系资源，发挥各类学生组织特色，避免学生团体重复建设，提高学联整体效率等都起到了积极的作用。</span><span lang="EN-US"> </span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;&#xd;&#xa;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">代表常任，深化校园民主与夯实维权机制稳步推进。通过近三年来的探索、研究和试点，本次学代会将首次推出&ldquo;代表任期制&rdquo;，旨在落实学生代表在学代会开会、闭会期间的实际权力和义务，实现对学联工作和学联发展全程监督，及时收集同学意愿、解决校园民生问题。</span><span lang="EN-US"> </span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;&#xd;&#xa;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">关注时政，服务社会与感恩奉献有所作为。&ldquo;汶川大地震&rdquo;发生后，校学联联合校红十字会学生分会、</span><span lang="EN-US">30</span><span style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;&#xd;&#xa;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">余支院系研究生会、学生会，</span><span lang="EN-US">70</span><span style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&#xd;&#xa;&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">余支学生社团的同学们迅速行动起来，在</span><span lang="EN-US">5</span><span style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&#xd;&#xa;&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">月</span><span lang="EN-US">13</span><span style="font-family:&#xd;&#xa;宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">日之后的短短</span><span lang="EN-US">5</span><span style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;&#xd;&#xa;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">天时间内，筹集到善款</span><span lang="EN-US">170</span><span style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&#xd;&#xa;&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">余万元，让&ldquo;大爱之风&rdquo;吹遍交大校园。在北京奥运会中，有</span><span lang="EN-US">47</span><span style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&#xd;&#xa;&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">名交大学子承担并出色的完成了北京和上海赛区的志愿服务任务。</span><span lang="EN-US"> </span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;&#xd;&#xa;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">放眼世界，国际交流与区域影响显著提升。</span><span lang="EN-US">2006</span><span style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;&#xd;&#xa;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">年，交大学联发起并组织了三届&ldquo;华人青年领袖论坛&rdquo;，邀请海内外知名大学的华人学生会主席共聚上海，关注时政，畅谈使命。今天，华领论坛已成功举办三届，先后邀请近两百位青年领袖，并已发展成为国内外颇具影响的学生交流舞台。</span><span lang="EN-US"> </span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;</p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family:宋体;&#xd;&#xa;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">在这些变化、进步与提升中，交大学联形成了华人青年领袖论坛、交大人节、联合杯辩论赛、高雅艺术进校园、</span><span lang="EN-US">VOS</span><span style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;&#xd;&#xa;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">毕业生晚会等一大批高水平的品牌活动；涌现出了全国优秀学生干部标兵浦栋麟、上海市新长征突击手标兵方曦等一批品格优秀、能力卓越的学生干部；在校园内外建立了广泛而坚强的群众基础，团结和带领全体青年学生，在学校管理中发挥主人翁作用，努力推动学校建设发展。</span></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>

